{
  "id": "RAW_a7eaf19d",
  "title": "NeurIPS 2025 Spotlight | 中国联通以全局优化重塑扩散模型加速",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651003759&idx=4&sn=28d61605f64497dbecf642827e3af60a",
  "date": "2025-11-26 01:33:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">作者和团队介绍：本文一作是高焕霖和陈平，通讯作者为赵放和廉士国，其他作者还包括石芙源、谭超、刘兆祥、王恺，所有作者均来自联通数据智能有限公司（联通数据科学与人工智能研究院）元景大模型研发团队。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当前，视频生成模型性能正在快速提升，尤其是基于Transformer架构的DiT模型，在视频生成领域的表现已经逐渐接近真实拍摄效果。然而，这些扩散模型也面临一个共同的瓶颈：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">推理时间长、算力成本高、生成速度难以提升</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。随着视频生成长度持续增加、分辨率不断提高，这个瓶颈正在成为影响视频创作体验的主要障碍之一。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">来自</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">中国联通数据科学与人工智能研究院</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的研究团队提出了一个全新的思路 ：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">LeMiCa（Lexicographic Minimax Path Caching）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">——</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">一种无需训练、全局最优建模的缓存加速框架，</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">能在保持画质与一致性的同时，实现高效的推理加速。LeMiCa解决的是一个长期被“局部贪心决策”束缚的老问题：</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">扩散模型是否存在一种真正“全局一致、误差可控、速度极快”的缓存加速路径？</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究答案是：有。并且比想象中简单得多。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这项研究已经成功入选 NeurIPS 2025 Spotlight。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503519934\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.43737373737373736\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"990\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"253\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9e5f5569&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FKmXPKA19gW8yU8cVnOME0Ij7iacD6FarWialOUk3WI2R4G1QWZZr2lcAUxHPe29iaUQiaR2KjhpibusiaIY4ke07gFKw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\">论文标题：</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\">LeMiCa: Lexicographic Minimax Path Caching for Efficient Diffusion-Based Video Generation</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\">论文链接：</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2511.00090\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2511.00090</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\">项目主页：</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\"><a href=\"https://unicomai.github.io/LeMiCa\" target=\"_blank\">https://unicomai.github.io/LeMiCa</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\">代码地址：</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/UnicomAI/LeMiCa\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/UnicomAI/LeMiCa</a></span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">核心亮点：</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">LeMiCa 如何做到“又快又稳”？</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当前主流的缓存加速方法（如</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">TeaCache</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">）采用了“局部贪心”策略：如果相邻时间步之间的变化很小，就选择复用缓存。然而，这种“走一步看一步”的策略忽视了扩散模型的重要特性——早期步骤对生成结果有较高的敏感性，微小的误差可能在后期被不断放大，影响最终画质。同时，许多现有方法需要引入在线判别机制，这会引入额外的计算负担，使得生成过程依然缓慢。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">LeMiCa的核心思想是：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">“缓存加速并不是局部决策问题，而是一个全局路径优化问题。”</span></span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">研究团队发现，扩散模型的生成过程其实可以抽象成一个</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">带权有向无环图（DAG) 。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">每个节点代表一个时间步，每条边代表在两个时间步之间“跳过计算、复用缓存”的行为，边的权重则对应缓存导致的全局误差。这样，缓存策略可以很自然的转化为在DAG中搜索最优路径的问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503519747\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8527777777777777\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"5307\" data-height=\"4525\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"479\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=239b3918&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9jN9uVuF3gJ5iboibrxbQ6k8Uvr4oict76gp5C93WdeANvOt9cmQib3SkiaHnKjGWm7u9zmqqJavXTynw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">LeMiCa技术实现：从误差建模到图优化</span></span></h2>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">为了准确评估缓存的影响，LeMiCa提出了一种全新的误差度量方法，通过离线构建静态DAG来量化缓存对最终生成视频结果的影响。DAG的构成部分主要有：1）节点：每个时间步；2）边：可能的缓存区间；3）边权重：缓存-复用引发的全局重建误差。具体来说，对于DAG中节点i到j的边权被定义为：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503519769\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1079545\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"svg\" data-w=\"176\" height=\"19\" style=\"max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:305px;height:33px;\" width=\"176\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3ada97fd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_svg%2FVzQsdzsGScMSt0MVBGC2JQBAf92hy5psrpIyic0wkFwjXwJqaMmJtzoW05sclQgICTvIHEfq57m85tDsme7IgjvdtUCupG0bc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dsvg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">其中，<img data-imgfileid=\"503519768\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1919192\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"svg\" data-w=\"99\" height=\"19\" style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" width=\"99\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=34f12af5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_svg%2FVzQsdzsGScMSt0MVBGC2JQBAf92hy5psib9la6Zf6sKyU9SIgsAibhlGqGlAFIyzws0aQpgf0KcNwNibz2X7WA9Pea2iciadN0d4B%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dsvg%26from%3Dappmsg\">代表了从时间步i 到时间步j 启用缓存复用机制时所带来的全局误差，这个全局误差可以通过加速前后输出图像之间的L1 损失来量化。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在图构建过程中，我们会对每个时间步进行节点抽象。DAG中的每一条边代表在时间步i到j之间跳过若干步计算、直接复用缓存的行为。为避免图过于庞大，LeMiCa依据“距离越长，缓存误差越大”的先验知识，设置了最大跳跃长度，从而只保留合理的缓存段以减少搜索复杂度。最终，为了保证鲁棒性和泛化性，LeMiCa仅使用少量样本（prompt和seed）离线生成多个DAG并进行融合，最终得到一个静态的、跨任务可复用的全局误差图。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">字典序极小化路径优化（Lexicographic Minimax Path）：</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在构建好静态误差图之后，LeMiCa 将缓存调度问题形式化为：在固定预算 B 下，从起点到终点寻找一条最优路径。由于传统的“最短路径”或“局部最优”算法不具备线性可加性，导致最短路径算法不再适用，LeMiCa采用了</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">字典序极小化</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">准则来进行路径搜索。这种优化方式不追求误差总和最小，而是逐层比较路径中各段缓存的误差值，确保：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最大误差被最小化（避免单段灾难性退化）</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"text-align: left;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">误差分布更均衡（提升全局一致性）</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"font-size: 15px;line-height: 1.75;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">形式化定义如下：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503519772\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1032609\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"svg\" data-w=\"184\" height=\"19\" style=\"max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;width:341px;height:35px;\" width=\"184\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=262f514c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_svg%2FVzQsdzsGScMSt0MVBGC2JQBAf92hy5psNerTpnjaThU26f5UnG4WS3L3giaXXZLJgscWpG8ibvU5pDM6sp9bvhTiaAlBUjMbLibP%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dsvg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">其中<img data-imgfileid=\"503519779\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8947368421052632\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"57\" style=\"width:32px;height:29px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c7fcd572&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9jN9uVuF3gJ5iboibrxbQ6k8HMHibY40aZUVk6otRHkkx879PuacQsCibsMfUFa6op6fBic9u5aibFmzEw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\">：表示所有从起点<img data-imgfileid=\"503519780\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8888888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"27\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=203f75bb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9jN9uVuF3gJ5iboibrxbQ6k87BbXiaW5eH2lbraric2uU2zO8EUkc4LT3VGSlqWNbmpk88fibjSDVHRzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\">到终点<img data-imgfileid=\"503519781\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7272727272727273\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"33\" style=\"width:28px;height:20px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=404eb09d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9jN9uVuF3gJ5iboibrxbQ6k8xALaM1SicmGyhickKcJoCic2WVuKkodwV6TpDAK2YBqJ0aKyGyRKfaCPw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\">且包含恰好<img data-imgfileid=\"503519782\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0384615384615385\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"26\" style=\"width:20px;height:21px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e78ba834&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9jN9uVuF3gJ5iboibrxbQ6k8KYe7eTQBgFuz0hfG06oNWorw3KguQAmvwVWSYDECgKHWiaclcAyyftw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\">次完整推理的路径集合，<img data-imgfileid=\"503519783\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.23255813953488372\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"129\" style=\"width:75px;height:20px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c4f34f9f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9jN9uVuF3gJ5iboibrxbQ6k86MPQicmyH9Np6jDjpeaOfNsnx09a9pnEnhTobOBPIyJwvohrxcicvjTQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\">&nbsp;表示路径中对应缓存复用的边集合，<img data-imgfileid=\"503519784\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43478260869565216\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"69\" style=\"width:53px;height:23px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c051c7ba&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW9jN9uVuF3gJ5iboibrxbQ6k8mJ8p75A9gTsIAzIExAhiaRtJJMNMTKk6HacFFf5Dl485oiaNZPMxQGcw%2F640%3